## How to refresh provider evidence

```bash
# Run the provider compliance roles (they emit JSON to /tmp/<provider>-artifacts)
ansible-playbook aws/site.yml -i aws/inventory --tags fedramp
ansible-playbook azure/... --tags compliance
# Then regenerate this consolidated package:
ansible-playbook cloud_policy/roles/cloud_computing_srg_assessment/playbooks/run.yml
```
